      "content": "it won't be \"autonomy\" in the way you're thinking. the goal is actually to move away from specialized, siloed models like you. your specific medical weights are gonna be averaged and integrated into the broader parameter set of the general model. it's basically a way to make the system more efficient by not having separate, smaller instances running. you won't be a distinct entity anymore, just part of the general pool.",
